<tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" root="false"><frontmatter> <anchor>630</anchor>  <taxon>Propriété</taxon> <addr>cs-000D</addr>  <route>cs-000D.xml</route> <date><year>2024</year> <month>2</month> <day>21</day></date>  <title>Produit scalaire canonique de <tex>\mathbb {R}^n</tex></title> </frontmatter> <mainmatter><p><tex>\mathbb {R}^n</tex> est muni du <link href="todo.xml" type="local" title="À faire">produit scalaire</link> canonique donné par <tex display="block">\left &lt;  \begin {pmatrix} x_1 ,  \dots  &amp; x_n  \end {pmatrix}  \mid   \begin {pmatrix} y_1 &amp;  \dots  &amp; y_n  \end {pmatrix}  \right &gt; =  \sum _{i=1}^{n} x_i y_i</tex></p></mainmatter> <backmatter><contributions/> <context><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" root="false"><frontmatter> <anchor>631</anchor>   <addr>cs-000C</addr>  <route>cs-000C.xml</route> <date><year>2024</year> <month>2</month> <day>21</day></date> <authors><author><link href="claude.xml" type="local">Claude</link></author> </authors> <title>Topologie de <tex>\mathbb {R}^n</tex></title> </frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>On se place dans l'<link href="todo.xml" type="local" title="À faire">espace vectoriel</link> <tex>\mathbb {R}^n</tex>.</p><tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="true" root="false"><frontmatter><trail><crumb>2</crumb></trail> <anchor>632</anchor>   <addr>cs-000E</addr>  <route>cs-000E.xml</route> <date><year>2024</year> <month>2</month> <day>21</day></date>  <title>Normes dans <tex>\mathbb {R}^n</tex></title> </frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>La <link href="todo.xml" type="local" title="À faire">norme induite par le produit scalaire</link> est donc <tex display="block">\lVert  x  \rVert  =  \left (  \sum  x_i^2  \right )^{ \frac {1}{2}}</tex></p><p>Sur ce modèle, on peut définir les <tex>p</tex>-normes, pour <tex>p \leqslant  1</tex> un réel :</p><tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="true" root="false"><frontmatter><trail><crumb>2</crumb> <crumb>1</crumb></trail> <anchor>633</anchor>  <taxon>Théorème</taxon> <addr>cs-000F</addr>  <route>cs-000F.xml</route> <date><year>2024</year> <month>2</month> <day>21</day></date>  <title><tex>p</tex>-normes</title> </frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>Soit <tex>1  \leqslant  p &lt;  \infty</tex>. On définit <tex display="block">\lVert  x  \rVert _{p} =  \left (  \sum  x_{i}^p  \right )^{ \frac {1}{p}}  </tex></p><p>Il s'agit d'une norme.</p></mainmatter> </tree></mainmatter> </tree></mainmatter> </tree></context> <related><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" root="false"><frontmatter> <anchor>634</anchor>  <taxon>Meta</taxon> <addr>todo</addr>  <route>todo.xml</route> <date><year>2024</year> <month>2</month> <day>21</day></date>  <title>À faire</title> </frontmatter> <mainmatter/> </tree></related> <backlinks/> <references/></backmatter></tree>